Hi
Extensions are implemented in HubSpot extension.
The specification is the ability to match contact records with custom object records.
Check the checkbox and press the matching button to link the two records.
Currently, the checkboxes have to be checked one at a time, but we would like to be able to check and match them all at once.
But I can't implement the function to check checkboxes in batch.
Does the onChange() function of checkbox in HubSpot not reflect the change state even if the state value changes?
